title: Jotunblood - Sunsetter (Dubstep) [2014] mp3[320]
description:
After a long and arduous process, I'm finally able to release my new album. It's been nearly two years since my last one, so I hope you all enjoy it.


You can always check me out on Soundcloud, Youtube, Bandcamp, Facebook, and wherever else I've made an account and probably forgot about.

Please share this as much as you'd like, just give me a shout-out :)


As always, thank you for your support!
